'''Dil Jan Khan''' ([[Urdu]]: '''<U+062F><U+0644> <U+062C><U+0627><U+0646> <U+062E><U+0627><U+0646>''') (born [[April]], [[1934]]) is a former President of [[International Narcotics Control Board]] of [[UNODC]]. Ethnically, he is a [[Marwat]] and was born in Dirstrict [[Lakki Marwat]] of [[Pakistan]]. He joined Police Service of Pakistan on 21st January 1961. Dil Jan has also worked as an Inspector General of Police and on a number of other important positions in the civil bureaucracy of Pakistan.

